title: Curad Performance Series Ironman Antibacterial Bandages, Extreme Hold Adhesive Technology, Assorted Variety Pack Includes Standard, XL, Finger & Knuckle Fabric Bandages, 50 Count
description: CURAD Performance Series is the lineup of rugged supports, wraps, kinesiology tape and bandages made to withstand the demands of active people. Every solution is designed to last through the toughest workouts and competition. Made to stay on through rain, mud and movement, CURAD Performance Series bandages feature antibacterial pads, flexible fabric and tenacious adhesive to give you comfort with dirt and germ protection when the going gets tough. Not for use on delicate and sensitive skin.
